{"tid":1562790,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗良心小店！蕃茄師兄！","createTime":"2019-09-12T07:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T07:18:47.000Z","uid":229940,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6412d378814d2e41c0a65a75b04a33ca3ca7b869","tid":1562790,"uid":229940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"話說今日去咗深水埗食晏晝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁啱見到依間良心小店！蕃茄師兄！<br />\n二話不說即刻拎位，但放返時間好多人。<br />\n企左門口等一陣，入邊姐姐即刻拎啲扇出嚟派。<br />\n人間有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入到去叫左碗半滑蛋牛肉米線，一送到黎已經聞到好濃郁嘅蕃茄味。<br />\n飲咗啖湯即刻知道係新鮮蕃茄煲出嚟，杰撻撻好正！<br />\n啲蛋夠滑，牛肉又多又唔會un<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇得頂！下次即一定會搵多啲朋友一齊嚟食！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0WqhBB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0WqhBB4.jpg&h=b4c5da38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b6dbf55d4a2edc3d4d8a706c48143680e3aa7ea","tid":1562790,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e38f86288e8b59967c2f0e344acf94f605b4325","tid":1562790,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:03:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t